  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Kaki Bukit + Islandwide<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> <strong>$2,000+ + $190 MVC</strong> per month<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> <strong>Monday – Friday, 8:00 AM – 5:30 PM</strong><br /><strong>Job Scope:</strong><br />• Deliver parcels and stock across assigned routes.<br />• Likely includes <em>delivery of parcels, letters, documents (under 20 kg).</em><br /><strong>Vehicle:</strong> <em>Van provided (company vehicle), </em><em><strong>cannot be brought home</strong></em>.<br /></p><p></p><p></p><p><br /></p><p><em>\"This is in partnership with the Employment and Employability Institute Pte Ltd (“e2i”).</em></p><p><em>e2i is the empowering network for workers and employers seeking employment and employability solutions. e2i serves as a bridge between workers and employers, connecting with workers to offer job security through job-matching, career guidance and skills upgrading services, and partnering employers to address their manpower needs through recruitment, training, and job redesign solutions. e2i is a tripartite initiative of the National Trades Union Congress set up to support nation-wide manpower and skills upgrading initiatives. By applying for this role, you consent to RMA Groups’s PDPA and </em><u><em>e2i’s PDPA</em></u><em>.\"</em></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
